	<h1>
		Online Ward Survey
	</h1>
	<br />
	<p>
		When a new member user registers on the website, they are taken to the member survey
		page. Here they will fill out questions that will help leadership get to know them
		better and help leadership have good information to make inspired calling decisions.
		<br />
		<br />
		Portions of this information are given to members of the ward to help them with
		their callings. Those permissions are granted by members of the bishopric and no
		unauthorized person will have access to a member's information.
		<br />
		<br />
		Some of the questions indcude:
		<ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 10px">
			<li>Personal Information</li>
			<li>Church Information (Mission, Callings, Past Leaders)</li>
			<li>Other Information (School, Institute, Activity Ideas)</li>
		</ul>
	</p>
